instructions: On your computer, go to Hangouts at hangouts.google.com or in Gmail . Click the Call tab . In the search box, type a phone number or name. To enter an international country code, click the menu or type it into the search box (for example, +55 for Brazil). Click the phone number or person's name that you want to call. To enter an extension, click the Dialpad . To end a call, close the Hangout window, or click End call . The call will also end if you run out of calling credit.
On your computer, go to Hangouts at hangouts.google.com or in Gmail . Click the Phone tab . Click New conversation and then Add credit . Your call history will show up in Google Voice .
